### Import Global Variables
@import ./globals.http

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiPrefix = /api/v1

### Health Check - Basic
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - With detailed info
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/health?detailed=true
Accept: application/json

### Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### API Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/documentation
Accept: text/html
